Ultra light-weight blogging engine that is very easy to implement.
This project has been written for 'The Queue' feed in Read (http://readapp.net)

Requirements: PHP 5 and a MySQL Server

What does it do?

1. Blog: parses XML -> HTML (last 25 entries)
2. Post a new Entry: Generates a .XML Feed in UTF-8 -> Updates Blog
3. Text-only

